race.comment: SKY SPRINGER (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (29.17) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and looks hard to stop. GLOWING ETHICS (2) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 0.8 lengths (29.14) at this track. One of the main contenders. MCIVOR JEWELS (7) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (29.09) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading chance. DESTINI REBEL (6) is worth including after a top-three finish at big odds most recently.
